  "body": "<center>\n\n<img src=\"https://ewanhowell.com/assets/images/resourcepacks/better-bows/logo.webp?rnd=0.04231423571090187\" width=\"519\" alt=\"Better Bows Logo\"><br>\n\n## The bow improvement resource pack!\n<br>\n\n[View the pack on my website!](https://ewanhowell.com/resourcepacks/better-bows)\n<br><br>\n\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/WujjBzwk00g \" width=\"600\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe><br><br><br>\n\nThis pack remodels both the bow and crossbow to have the arrow 3D, like how it is in the world after you fire it!\n\nThe crossbow also supports showing 3D firewords, spectral arrows, and tipped arrows!\n\nWhen you have multishot, you will see three arrows at once in the crossbow!\n<br><br><br>\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/IPRL7R5J/images/afd710a206d0869ca30b37322dbc116b3c0cbfbd.png\" width=\"600\" alt=\"Bow\"><br><br>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/IPRL7R5J/images/485c137686ff93cc3f782aaf6245267592db1231.png\" width=\"600\" alt=\"Crossbow\"><br><br>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/IPRL7R5J/images/dda80fc516e46a2f4084b6121cb6db52abc9b1d3.png\" width=\"600\" alt=\"Aiming Bow\"><br><br>\n\n⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯⎯\n\n[<img src=\"https://ewanhowell.com/assets/images/icons/discord.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\"> \n<br>\n<u>Join my Discord Server!</u>]( https://discord.ewanhowell.com/)\n<br><br>\n[<img src=\"https://ewanhowell.com/assets/images/icons/discord.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\"> \n<br>\n<u>Join the Resource Pack Development Discord Server!</u>]( https://resourcepacks.ewanhowell.com/)\n<br><br>\n[<img src=\"https://ewanhowell.com/assets/images/icons/youtube.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\"> \n<br>\n<u>Subscribe on YouTube!</u>]( https://www.youtube.com/@EwanHowell)\n<br><br>\n[<img src=\"https://ewanhowell.com/assets/images/icons/twitter.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\"> \n<br>\n<u>Follow me on Twitter!</u>]( https://twitter.com/ewanhowell5195)\n<br><